==English==
===Etymology===
From the surname of [[w:John Wayne Bobbitt|John Wayne Bobbitt]], or rather from his wife, Lorena Leonor Gallo de Bobbitt, who cut off her husband John's penis while he slept.

===Transitive verb===
'''Bobbitt''' ('''Bobbitts''', '''Bobbitting''', '''Bobbitted''', '''Bobbittized''')

# {{informal}} To cut off the [[penis]] of another.
#:''Watch out, she might bobbitt you as you sleep.''